Package com.example.donotredeem

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.example.donotredeem.User
public class User extends Object
Represents a user profile with information such as username, password, email, contact details, bio, profile picture, and social connections (followers, following, requests, mood references, etc.).

      username - The username of the user.
      password - The password of the user.
      email - The email address of the user.
      dob - The user's date of birth.
      contact - The contact information of the user.
      bio - The biography or description of the user.

    • User

      public User(String username, String bio, String profilePictureUrl, List<String> followerList, List<String> followingList, List<String> requests, List<com.google.firebase.firestore.DocumentReference> moodRefs, int moods)
      Constructor to initialize a user with followers, following, requests, mood references, and profile picture.
      Parameters:
      username - The username of the user.
      bio - The biography of the user.
      profilePictureUrl - The URL of the user's profile picture.
      followerList - The list of followers.
      followingList - The list of users being followed.
      requests - The list of follow requests.
      moodRefs - List of document references for mood events.
      moods - The count of moods associated with the user.
